$BBOLD b)$EBOLD The odd component of \(x(t)\) is shown by \(x_o(t)\).
$PAR
$SPACE $SPACE $SPACE 1) Find the equation for \(x_o(t)\).$BR
$SPACE $SPACE $SPACE $SPACE $SPACE $SPACE \(x_o(t)=\)\{ans_rule(35)\} $BR

