$PAR
$SPACE $SPACE $SPACE 2) From the figures 1 to 4 shown below, select the graph that matches \(x_o(t)\).$BR
$SPACE $SPACE $SPACE $SPACE $SPACE $SPACE Figure: \{$choice2->menu()\} $BR

$PAR
